{
  "stem": "24130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would sit-- would sit on the steps-- and he-- he belonged to the [NON-ENGLISH]-- and he says-- her name was Anna-- Anna, if you step up those steps, I'm going to shoot you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a gun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she says, you are crazy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not going to go and make fire for the kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're cold.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then milk the cow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She says, you better don't step-- go on the steps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He took out the gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this girl was afraid, so she didn't come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember, she spit in his face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it gave me satisfaction that she-- she did this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this-- but when the Hungarians came in, they were fighting the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was right in front of our house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were shooting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remembered my father says, we should lay down, because the bullets were flying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was so scared, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I says, oh, the war is here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt that the war is not far away anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war is here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the Hungarian came in, my father says, they a little bit better than the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least these are-- So these [NON-ENGLISH] were rounded up, and they-- they killed them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Hungarians killed these-- these young boys, a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the priest from our town also belonged to the [NON-ENGLISH], but he came home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let him come home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was before the Hungarians occupied.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had, already, the peasants turned against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I felt that-- we felt it very strong, you know the anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were some people that they say-- I remembered this boy that came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Yoji.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
